:::


## The Model


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
model_ancova <- lm(post ~ drug + pre, data = df_sas)

model_glance <- model_ancova |>
  glance()
model_tidy <- model_ancova |>
  tidy()
model_glance |>
  gt()
```

